      Speech
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Jeremy Wright speaking at the launch of the Online Harms White Paper
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The speech was delivered on Monday 8 April 2019 at the British Library
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

